LVGL menuconfig:

- Revisit fonts later
- Can swap X/Y and invert X/Y in menuconfig
- Touch on I2C 0
- SPI2_HOST
- Backlight on/off logic level, PWM, IO pin
- I2C port pins for LVGL

lvgl_esp32_drivers is old and doesn't support ESP32, forks that look promising:

- https://github.com/VitorAlho/lvgl_esp32_drivers
- https://github.com/artemisoftnian/lvgl_esp32_drivers
- https://github.com/BunnySakura/lvgl_esp32_drivers
- https://github.com/COP-AMACO/lvgl_esp32_drivers
